high_descs: walk forwards to the sink on the right at the end of the room just up ahead
grab the tomato out of the sink
turn around and walk over to the stove on the right side of the room
place the tomato inside of the microwave above the stove, let it cook and then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the end of the room, then take a left and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room
place the tomato inside of the fridge there
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved tomato inside of the fridge

high_descs: Go to the sink in front of you.
Pick up a tomato in the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go toward the stove, then look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside and heat it up, then take the tomato out.
Turn around and go to the wall, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink on the left.
Pick up the tomato inside the sink in the middle.
Turn around, walk to the white stove on the right, and look up at the microwave.
Put the tomato inside the microwave above the stove, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the heated tomato inside the fridge on the top shelf to the left of the loaf of bread and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a fridge.
